## 🚀 Quick Start

### 1. Clone

bash
git clone https://github.com/yourname/heypocket-export.git
cd heypocket-export

Run Setup
POWERSHELL
.\install.ps1

POWERSHELL
setx HEYPOCKET_API_TOKEN "your-token"
setx MS_TRANSLATOR_KEY "your-key"
setx MS_TRANSLATOR_REGION "westus2"

RUN
run en,fr,es

OUTPUT
data/output/*.enex

