# 🧠 Short “Why It Matters” Section

```md
## 🧠 Why This Exists

This tool bridges:

- 🎙️ Real-world speech capture (Pocket)
- 🌐 Cloud translation (Azure)
- 📝 Structured knowledge systems (ENEX / Evernote)

Allowing users to:

✔ Record in any language  
✔ Translate instantly  
✔ Store as structured, searchable notes  

## ⚠️ Known Quirk (Handled)

PowerShell may collapse single-item JSON arrays into objects.
This tool forces correct array format to ensure API reliability.
